chage
===========
Compress and uncompress
tar -cvf filaname.tar <dir/file to be compressed>
tar -czvf filename.tar.gz <directory>      making a tar.gz file directly
gzip filename.tar                          gzip a tar file
gunzip filename.tar                        Extracting a gzip file
tar -zxvf filename.tar.gz                  extracting a tar.gz file
============
tee COMMAND
echo "192.168.100.1 Server1" | sudo tee -a /etc/hosts
